A '''crackhead''' is a person who is [[drug addiction|addicted]] to [[crack cocaine]]. The term is also used as an [[insult]], to describe anyone who seems to be acting foolishly. "Crackheads" appeared in great numbers during the [[1980s]], as crack cocaine became more available, cheaper, and of higher potency than other forms of [[cocaine]]. Crack addicts were and are a largely [[urban]] phenomenon. Those labeled as crackheads are also associated with [[homelessness]].

